{"tid":557392,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞] 《執放》 原：關楚耀 - 《飢餓遊戲》","createTime":"2018-02-11T10:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T14:57:02.000Z","uid":122380,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3da42ec182fb76036dee186f0f0d45d480693176","tid":557392,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:06:41.000Z","msg":"原唱：關楚耀 - 《飢餓遊戲》<br />\n原詞：陳詠謙<br />\n原曲：Howie@Dear Jane<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tF8GrlBWXe8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtF8GrlBWXe8&d=CNsDQD3KAHpJUnmXxIKdPtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=54bd9e32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tF8GrlBWXe8</a><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n&ldquo;唔好再咁留意佢喇&ldquo; <br />\n&ldquo;為個咁既人值得咩&ldquo;<br />\n &ldquo;放手喇&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n好似成日都聽人咁講<br />\n但有時愈努力放低，反而愈執著<br />\nーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー<br />\n《執放》   <br />\n<br />\n改詞:碧落<br />\n<br />\n流沙中栽花不發 逢春亦未萌芽<br />\n無心的不施牽掛 寒冬中枯化<br />\n直到你的優雅 燃亮我的天下<br />\n但我共你 亦終差一線嗎<br />\n<br />\n情歌當中的優美 如今漸漸無期<br />\n藏於沙堆的憶記 誰不甘拋棄<br />\n惦掛你的香氣 尋覓世間天地<br />\n密友在說 像小狗跟尾<br />\n<br />\n誰說著前事會完盡 回憶雖美也須葬殉<br />\n為了淡化 便徹夜用神 將風光蹂躪<br />\n而我愈忘掉你 無奈更執著 無奈更急進<br />\n若風聲不再叫囂 舊傷疤應會結焦 不相信<br />\n<br />\n誰甘於沙堆風化 殘花亦剩餘芽<br />\n無相戀者的資格 仍忠心牽掛<br />\n直到你的出嫁 蠶食我的天下<br />\n密友在說 別執於不化<br />\n<br />\n誰說著前事會完盡 回憶雖美也須葬殉<br />\n為了淡化 在赤地自焚 春色的餘燼<br />\n而我愈忘掉你 無奈更執著 無奈更急進<br />\n若風聲不再叫囂 舊傷疤應會結焦 不相信<br />\n<br />\n閒聊時同伴話我應該結束<br />\n落花之中折福 徹去斷送<br />\n明瞭前塵如幻影不可再碰 留杯中找放縱 這情種<br />\n<br />\n能放下才是算緣盡 回憶雖美也須葬殉<br />\n若要淡化 在雪地浪遊 幽香不盈袖<br />\n如結局忘掉你 忘掉過執著 如夢碎一瞬<br />\n待風聲不再叫囂 舊傷疤終會結焦 終深信<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n搵唔到人唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  求其錄左個demo 巴絲禁落去之前請做去心理準備 內有噪音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.joox.com/common_redirect.html?page=ksong_production&amp;id=KWORK_2_105450523_1518176375294&amp;appshare=iphone&amp;backend_country=hk&amp;lang=zh_TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.joox.com%2Fcommon_redirect.html%3Fpage%3Dksong_production%26id%3DKWORK_2_105450523_1518176375294%26appshare%3Diphone%26backend_country%3Dhk%26lang%3Dzh_TW&d=CNsDQD3KAHpJUnmXxIKdPtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=bcbb8c19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.joox.com/common_redirect.html?page=ksong_production&amp;id=KWORK_2_105450523_1518176375294&amp;appshare=iphone&amp;backend_country=hk&amp;lang=zh_TW</a>"},{"pid":"1d7592bdeced6e5468833e350fd02ebf4901c492","tid":557392,"uid":41326,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361e50a08a82fd781b1c249e6f4f16dcdafafd06","tid":557392,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed21c8516609eab2da16f712f76887d28d3675df","tid":557392,"uid":126519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:31:38.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"b1746098fbc872c01cb2aefb6e38dbee2696956d","tid":557392,"uid":10821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a3251756e216bc07b390e6540ec4fabb211d01","tid":557392,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d7592bdeced6e5468833e350fd02ebf4901c492","tid":557392,"uid":41326,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"挽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df8a2ed80f9a23d9099a9d26770d8074f1534c9","tid